latestPosts.caption:
Dibrugarh, get ready to spice up your cravings! 🌶️✨
Namma Chennai Dosa Express is finally here — serving up Kerela Parotta, Kaima Parotta, and a full-on South Indian feast! 🍛🍽️
Authentic flavors, homely vibes, and dishes that’ll make you say “Enna Rasa!” 😍

📍 KC Gogoi Path, Khaliamari (Opp. MDKG Science College)
📞 7550280537 / 6001589394

Come hungry, leave dosa-fied! 😋
